article_title: Q&A: Ald. Maurice Cheeks is bullish on the city’s tech sector
article_text:
Madison, WI (53711)

Today

Thunderstorms likely. High 81F. Winds SSE at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 90%..

Tonight

Thunderstorms early, then cloudy skies after midnight. Low 64F. Winds SSE at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 80%.

article_metadata.author: MIKE IVEY | The Capital Times | mivey@madison.com

og.description: Cheeks, recently named director of the Wisconsin Innovation Network, says Madison is a good place for startups to grow but access to investment capital remains a challenge here.
